SNG 27 (E)
MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2001-Cab(i)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 22nd July, 2001
31 Asadha, 1923 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from the 22nd July,
2001, -
Shri Nitish Kumar relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Agriculture. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of Minister
of Railways;
i)
ii)
UShri Ajit Singh assumed the charge of the office of Minister of Agriculture;
Shri Omar Abdullah relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Commerce and Industry and assumed the charge
of the office of Minister of State in the Ministry of External Affairs;
ii)
iv)
Shri Digvijay Singh relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Railways and assumed the charge of the office of
Minister of State in the Ministry of Commerce and Industry; and
v) Shri Krishnamaraju relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of External Affairs and assumed the charge of the
office of Minister of State in the Ministry of Defence.
(P.'Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary.
